column191: participantComments:"Each round I was predicting what would happen
column193: which color would ditch first. I suspected one or both would ditch much sooner and spend more rounds being angry and getting even with each other. One aspect that would make a difference would be to know whether they are competing for totals
column194: or just collaborating to maximize results
column195: before trying to predict whether either were angry at any point. Yellow was still smiling at the end
column196: so it seems like maybe they are on a co-op farm and its is not a matter of winners and losers."
